[~tedyu@apache.org] I think add this to HBase is well, but it maybe some trick if we add this to HDFS. Because I think we should fix this at the source of problem in HDFS.

{code}
   String str = uri.getScheme()+"://"+uri.getAuthority();
    this.uri = URI.create(str);
    if (uri.getPort() == -1) {
      String svcName = this.dfs.getCanonicalServiceName();
      int idx = svcName.indexOf(':');
      if (idx > 0) {
        str = str + svcName.substring(idx);
        this.uri = URI.create(str);
      }
    }
{code}

